WEBVTT

00:00.583 --> 00:04.231
Hong Kong is one of the most densely populated places on the planet.

00:04.681 --> 00:07.557
Its dramatic cityscapes cling to the hillsides...

00:07.685 --> 00:10.053
...and the edges of its spectacular harbor.

00:11.286 --> 00:16.185
Hong Kong is the embodiment of yin and yang, the Chinese concept of balance.

00:17.483 --> 00:22.495
It is filled with neighborhoods that resonate with Chinese and colonial tradition,...

00:22.985 --> 00:26.565
...while its soaring skylines look boldly towards the future.

00:27.247 --> 00:30.051
For visitors, Hong Kong offers some of the world's...

00:30.149 --> 00:34.253
...most intense shopping, sightseeing, and dining experiences,...

00:35.134 --> 00:39.180
...yet moments of stillness await at every turn.

